reviewText: this book breaks it all down i recomend this book i am still working on the greenhouse soon to start the whole process of fish, grow beds and pumps, oh my

Buy the book as a reference.  The presentation here is a taped version of a conference.
You can hear the speaker, and every gurgle of water she drinks, but the camera fails
to focus on her powerpoints, which are too small to read or discern photos,
so is NOT a good source of information for the visual learner.
